    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‘Mistified’ is the debut game from SpiceBound Studios. A fiendishly tricksy grid based puzzle game where your presence in a strange land will guide the lost souls of creatures to a better place, or a worse one. Their fate is decided by your success or failure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/cb54aa4a6fdac9bffcfb20f18ed76878.avif?t=1744918972\" width=650 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve 150+ expertly designed puzzles and dig deeper to uncover further challenges that will keep you puzzling as you forge ahead throughout this charming 2D world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the world map by manipulating the Giant Maps pet rabbit</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use sounds, such as your own footsteps, to guide creatures out of harm's way and into salvation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/7fccaa068e7feda5da7553755db76fd8.poster.avif?t=1744918972\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/7fccaa068e7feda5da7553755db76fd8.webm?t=1744918972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/7fccaa068e7feda5da7553755db76fd8.mp4?t=1744918972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make use of the spirit mist to transport objects or alter its path to change the direction of the flow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stomp down the dark claws to clear out a safe route.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a select bunch of handcrafted songs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150+ Puzzles using a combination of:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different animals, each with their own reactions and interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 different types of log, from standard to polarising.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A HAND-full of traps that want to eat the souls of the lost and occasionally lend a helping HAND.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rivers, and their many PITfalls and uses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/4a5cdc76e180aaa388107c1659fc6a3e.poster.avif?t=1744918972\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/4a5cdc76e180aaa388107c1659fc6a3e.webm?t=1744918972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/4a5cdc76e180aaa388107c1659fc6a3e.mp4?t=1744918972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join our Community to stay up to date with news and puzzles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
